    ```

    **Deprecated Block comment style (do not use):**
    ```kotlin
    /* ktlint-disable standard_no-wildcard-imports */
    import foo.*
    /* ktlint-enable standard_no-wildcard-imports */
    ```

    Ktlint will report violations for any usage of these deprecated directives. These violations cannot be suppressed."}

